snippet.title: The Sims 3 Island Paradise Launch Trailer
snippet.description: Make your escape with The Sims 3 Island Paradise. Run a five star luxury resort or travel the high seas in a custom-built houseboat. Dive beneath the water to explore and discover what may be waiting for your Sims. Discover Island Paradise!
